Package jdbc

Class DataBaseTransferExecutionInstructionsController

java.lang.Object
jdbc.DataBaseTransferExecutionInstructionsController
public class DataBaseTransferExecutionInstructionsController extends Object
DataBase Transfer Execution Instructions Controller In this class, queries will be made for the inventory update request process Queries: Get all operations workers from the database. Get all existing tasks from the database. Create a new execution task. Update an existing execution task.
